  "session": "2026RS",
  "identifier": "SB 199",
  "title": "AN ACT relating to pesticide labeling.",
  "abstract": "Create a new section of KRS Chapter 217 to establish that any pesticide registered with the Department of Agriculture, with an EPA approved label for use pursuant to the Federal Insecticide, Fungicide, and Rodenticide Act is deemed sufficient warning for the purposes of an action concerning duty to warn; amend KRS 217.544 to conform.",
